'Berhenti..'

00:20:38.360 --> 00:20:40.440 line:20%
'Saya melihat Mahima dan Rudra.  Ya..'

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:43.400 line:20%
'Preesha adalah masa lalu Rudraksh'

00:20:43.640 --> 00:20:45.480 line:20%
'dan aku hadiahnya.'

00:20:45.840 --> 00:20:47.200 line:20%
'Akulah masa depannya.'

