'Ya..'

00:20:53.360 --> 00:20:54.440 line:20%
'D-Dia benar.'

00:20:55.760 --> 00:20:57.440 line:20%
'Sekarang Mahima
sangat berarti bagiku.'

00:20:59.080 --> 00:21:00.120 line:20%
'Dia adalah segalanya bagiku.'

00:21:02.160 --> 00:21:03.360 line:20%
'Apa yang kami bagikan'

00:21:04.320 --> 00:21:05.320 line:20%
'adalah cinta sejati.'

00:21:05.600 --> 00:21:07.120 line:20%
“Kami sangat bahagia
satu sama lain.”

